OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FJapan swelters in worst    
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fheatwave since 1875        
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Japan is sweltering under the hottest  
OL,6, day yet of its worst heatwave for      
OL,7, almost 150 years.                      
OL,9,FThe blistering heat has drawn official 
OL,10,Fwarnings of a looming power shortage,  
OL,11,Fand led to calls for people to conserve
OL,12,Fenergy where possible.                 
OL,14,FBut the government is still advising   
OL,15,Fpeople to use use air conditioning to  
OL,16,Favoid heatstroke as cases of           
OL,17,Fhospitalisation rise with the heat.    
OL,19,FWeather officials warn the heat is     
OL,20,Flikely to continue in the coming days. 
